      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on manufactured solutions for Navier-Stokes and scalar transport must confirm expected convergence rates.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame Navier-Stokes and power-law hemolysis scalar transport. Observed order 1.97 (expected 2.0) on velocity; 1.89 on NIH scalar. Both within 6% of theoretical — acceptable for production meshes used in this COU."
