      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (2.1M, 6.8M, 18.4M cells) performed at 5 L/min / 4500 RPM. GCI_fine = 3.2% for NIH; GCI_fine = 1.8% for pressure rise. Asymptotic range confirmed (ratio 0.97). Fine mesh selected for all production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
