      "rationale": "PIV and hemolysis bench tests conducted at 37±0.5°C, Hct 33±1%, bovine blood viscosity 3.2±0.2 mPa·s. CFD inlet conditions set to measured mean values; tolerances propagated through UQ ensemble. Geometric fidelity confirmed via CT scan of test article vs. CAD nominal."
