      "rationale": "NIH MAPE = 8.3% across 5 operating points (all below 15% threshold). Pressure-rise RMS = 4.1 mmHg (threshold 8 mmHg). Velocity spatial correlation R = 0.94 (threshold 0.90). All three output comparison metrics satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
