      "rationale": "Bench experiments conducted on FDA generic pump geometry (identical CAD) with bovine blood at Hct 33%, spanning 7 operating points that bracket the 5 COU points. No geometric or fluid extrapolation required. Relevance score: High per Morrison Table 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
