      "rationale": "All production runs converged to scaled residuals < 5e-6 (continuity, momentum, k, omega, NIH scalar). Mass imbalance < 0.003% per impeller revolution. Convergence histories archived for all 5 COU operating points."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
