      "rationale": "Independent CFD analyst (not the original setup engineer) performed blind re-check of all boundary conditions, material properties, and solver settings against the experimental test report. Two minor discrepancies (inlet turbulence intensity) corrected prior to final production runs. No residual use-error flags."
