      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified for rotating internal flow; hemolysis power-law model coefficients sourced from peer-reviewed literature and sensitivity-tested.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on published benchmarks for centrifugal pump internal flows (Apel 2001, Hariharan 2011). Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger coefficients validated against 3 independent hemolysis datasets. Sensitivity of NIH to ±20% coefficient variation: <12% NIH change — within acceptable model-form uncertainty band."
    },
    {
