      "rationale": "Six uncertain inputs identified: viscosity, density, inlet velocity profile shape, rotational speed, power-law exponent alpha, power-law exponent beta. Distributions assigned from experimental characterization data. All six propagated through 500-sample Monte Carlo ensemble. Sobol indices computed; alpha and shear-exposure time are dominant contributors (S_total > 0.6)."
