      "rationale": "COU operating points: Re 4200–11800, flow coefficient phi 0.08–0.19. Validation experiment operating points: Re 3900–12400, phi 0.07–0.21. Maximum deviation: Re 7.1%, phi 10.5% at extreme boundary — borderline but accepted given overlapping envelopes and interpolation (not extrapolation) for all 5 COU points."
